    public class CyclicBufferList
extends AbstractList
implements List
    CyclicBuffer implementation that is Object generic, and implements the List interface. Original CyclicBuffer @author Ceki Gülcü This implementation (although there's very little change) @author Paul Smith <psmith@apache.org>
